	   <tr><td colspan=2>Ok on the Book its good but there is a better one that i found for cheap.&nbsp;&nbsp;Fine Antique Velvet Rose.  It has one less wis/int but it has Extended Range that will allow most wis based casters to but on a Velium Jasper Ring or another along those lines instead of the Moonstone Ring.  For Druids that kite its a must i just got it and i had 2 vel jas rings but i needed the moonstone so i ended up getting an extra 9 wis on it instead of the 3 i would have gotten with this book.  I am going to do the quest any way cause it will get better eventually, but i am a Focus Effect nut.  That is the #1 thing that i look for on items.  If you are looking for great druid items feel free to check me out or e-mail me if you need more item help.  <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/userinfo.html?char=292670" target=_new>http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/userinfo.html?char=292670</a>  <br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Sun Apr  6 20:53:21 2003</em><br>&nbsp;<br>Sleep is a sugestion, just like speed limits.<br>Xarra Portarra 44th Season Druid on Povar</td></tr>
